      Fields in io.atomix.core.profile declared as Profile 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static Profile Profile.CLIENT
      The client profile does not change the configuration of a node.
      static Profile Profile.CONSENSUS
      The consensus profile configures an Atomix instance with a Raft system partition and a multi-Raft data partition group.
      static Profile Profile.DATA_GRID
      The data grid profile configures an Atomix instance with a primary-backup system partition if no system partition is configured, and a primary-backup data partition group.
